    "properties": {
      "name": "Soaring Break",
      "description": "BASIC ATTACK: \nAn attack with up to 5 sequences that deals Physical DMG. As the controlled operator, Final Strike also deals  Stagger. \n\nDIVE ATTACK: \nBasic attack performed in mid-air becomes a dive attack that deals Physical DMG to nearby enemies. \n\nFINISHER: \nBasic attack performed near a Staggered enemy becomes a finisher attack that deals massive Physical DMG and recovers some SP."
    },
    "metadata": {
      "originId": "chenQianyu"
    }
  },
